{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act47side", "eventName": "未許之地", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "UR-5", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "注目禮", "storyInfo": "萊茵與高登的秘密雙雙暴露，展覽籌備陷入停滯，但負責審理特殊事故的聽證會遲遲沒有召開。斯凱帶人極力保護萊茵的“樹”，而古斯塔夫和梅蘭德都已強勢介入園區。然而此時，關鍵人物娜斯提卻不見了蹤影。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "38_g13_trimountlivingroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$act15_intro", "key": "$act15_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_inside", "channel": "f", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.3, "channel": "f", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*哥倫比亞粗口*天上飄著的那棵樹到底是怎麼回事？", "name": "憤怒的公司代表"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "展覽沒幾天就要開幕了，你數數它占了幾家公司的展位？萊茵生命並沒有申請上層的展示權限！", "name": "憤怒的公司代表"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一定是萊茵和管理局官員私相授受！昨晚我親眼看到了全程，園區負責人高登長官就在那棵樹上！", "name": "急切的公司代表"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前管理局局長古斯塔夫在廣播裡打包票，聲稱第二天早上一定會給我們一個交代，結果呢？", "name": "急切的公司代表"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都這個時候了，聽證會一點動靜都沒有，是不是故意拖時間！", "name": "急切的公司代表"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "f", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1", "duration": 0.8, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請各位稍安勿躁。", "name": "工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本次事件關乎數百家企業對園區的工程部和行政部的信任問題，我們需要時間謹慎處理，力求給各位最滿意的處理方案。", "name": "工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰要你們謹慎處理啊？", "name": "憤怒的公司代表"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上天的又不是第二個環形實驗室，有什麼大驚小怪的？", "name": "憤怒的公司代表"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "工程部負責的檢修早就暫停了，行政部的資格審查也結束了，現在這個節骨眼誰還會計較園區的部門負責人是否瀆職？", "name": "憤怒的公司代表"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但舉行聽證會是必要的監察流程……", "name": "工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要調查還是審判是你們的事，我們只想立刻知道聽證會的最終結果——", "name": "急切的公司代表"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這場必定能轟動哥倫比亞乃至整個泰拉的“天空生活展覽”，到底還辦不辦得成？", "name": "急切的公司代表"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "68_g9_treeplatform_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 2.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓開。", "name": "園區警衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-80", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sit_tatami", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我再說一遍，讓開。", "name": "園區警衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "斯凱"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們這些研究員，真當自己坐在這裡我就沒辦法動你們背後的非法設備了？", "name": "園區警衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在聽證會正式開始之前，它仍是萊茵生命的財產。再說了，非法設備？", "name": "斯凱"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "警衛先生，你難道沒認出來這只是一個“浮空種植單元”嗎？你身邊飄浮的那些樹苗，跟我們背後的這棵，沒有區別啊？", "name": "斯凱"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "強詞奪理……來人！", "name": "園區警衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "posfrom": "300,0", "posto": "30,0", "duration": 1.2}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-300,0", "posto": "-30,0", "duration": 1.2, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_529_1#1$1", "focus": "l", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……斯凱，我們人手不夠，如果對方動用強制手段，我們撐不了多久。", "name": "研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_529_1#1$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更何況我們也不知道身後的樹形裝置是否違規、有沒有危險。畢竟兩年前，克麗斯騰總轄不就是……", "name": "研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_529_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "posfrom": "0,-80", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只問你一個問題，身為一名科學家，你甘心把娜斯提主任的研究成果拱手讓人嗎？", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_529_1#1$1", "focus": "l", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，但……", "name": "研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_529_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就先行動起來，別讓自己後悔。", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，萊茵留駐園區的人數受限，我們的人還是太少了，要是……", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯凱先生，你是不是忘了我們也是萊茵生命的雇員？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1", "duration": 1.2, "isblock": "false"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2045_1#1$1", "duration": 1.2, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.7}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不想把你們牽扯進來。", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2045_1#1$1", "focus": "r", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是指聽證會的調查？別瞎擔心了，誣告和罪名哪一個我們見得少了？", "name": "體驗員B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早點叫我們過來，這群警衛說不定都上不了這個浮空平台。", "name": "體驗員A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2045_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼，從貧民窟徵集來的體驗員還想逞英雄？", "name": "園區警衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "藏匿非法設備、破壞他人財物、知情不報……光這些罪名就足以把你們打包送進監獄！", "name": "園區警衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2045_1#1$1", "focus": "r", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要不是娜斯提主任收留我，我現在可能已經在監獄裡了。", "name": "體驗員B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想動樹，就從我們身上跨過去。", "name": "體驗員A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2045_1#1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好……那就別怪我動手了！", "name": "園區警衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊茵研究員和體驗員組成的人牆死死攔著蠻橫的警衛，好事的圍觀者站在外圍，仰頭看著這棵突兀的“樹”。"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人群背後，一個陌生高大的黑影走過，腳步錚錚。"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodfloor_fts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2038_1#5$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7, "duration": 0.8, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2038_1#5$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是萊茵的……“樹”。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2038_1#5$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_hotel", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "channel": "crowd", "loop": "true", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_telephonering", "channel": "phone"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_telephone", "channel": "phone"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前輩，辛苦了。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別那麼見外，梅希亞。我前段時間一直都在休假，哪有工作讓我勞神？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您來參加聽證會？", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，梅蘭德緊急管理監督協會的徽章設計得還不錯，你也可以戴一個試試看。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的任務正式結束了？", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的任務才剛剛開始。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽您安排。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#6$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用著急。最近幾天真是意外不斷，除了娜斯提和高登·譚農之外，還有什麼我不知道的故事？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……沒有。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#7$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不錯。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "五分鐘之後纜車站見。這座園區令人眼花繚亂，我需要一位“當地導遊”，帶我好好參觀一下這座“螺旋槳天堂”。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_telephone", "channel": "phone"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（破碎的囈語）", "name": "拂哀菈"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_highheeledshoe_carpet_fts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.2, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，我應該提前把窗戶關起來的。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "街道上有公司代表和體驗員在遊行，聽證會拖得越久，他們就越不安。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openwindow", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "crowd", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_highheeledshoe_carpet_fts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拂哀菈女士，您好一點了嗎？", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（微弱的呼吸）", "name": "拂哀菈"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您的身體狀況很糟糕。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#4$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然您已經見到了娜斯提主任，不如我將您送回河谷——", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#11$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……不……", "name": "拂哀菈"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您又像昨晚一樣拒絕了我。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#12$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拂哀菈女士，接下來的幾天，園區會變得更加嘈雜。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#13$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再想離開，可就沒有那麼容易了。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#13$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_cellroomB", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1", "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#8$1", "duration": 0.8, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們又被抓起來了，連牢房編號都沒變！", "name": "奧克里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽證會的時間一改再改……你說他們是不是在找更多證據，打算數罪併罰？", "name": "奧克里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#2$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "話說在前頭，要是問起我們的身分，我一定會如實供述，你才是那個冒牌貨！", "name": "奧克里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#7$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，你怎麼都不說話啊，搞得我心裡發毛……", "name": "奧克里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#2$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實荒原上的移動監獄也能開發成不錯的旅遊景點。不過從外面闖進去和從裡面逃出來的難度完全不一樣，得小心一點。", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都到這種時候了，你還在評估旅遊路線嗎？", "name": "奧克里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "弄丟一個客人就算了，你還要把另一個關進牢裡？", "name": "奧克里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會找到那位女士，至於你，不用太擔心。", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#3$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼知道？", "name": "奧克里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有審訊、沒有身分核查、沒有出庭通知……你覺得那些警衛是在拖延時間幫我們編罪名？", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "奧克里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我倒覺得這恰好能證明——", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#3$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這場聽證會的主角，不是我們。", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#3$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "68_g7_airrestaurant", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#9$1", "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費爾南和奧克里被關進牢裡，小梅昨天晚上就不見了，註冊大廳的電話打不通，所有人都在找我跟娜斯提……", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#9$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，是時候把從管理局學的東西演給那個老東西看看了，不管他問什麼我都能給出解釋——我有什麼好怕的！", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#5$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，看來老狐狸的辦事效率沒有以前好了，到現在都沒人來審問我。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸，等等！", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#6$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_devicebeep", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還好……從終端上看，我現在的頭銜還是“螺旋槳天堂”的總長官。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#2$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2040_1#1$3"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘀——監測到“天空征服者”壓力過大，請注意健康風險，我們的目標在泰拉之外，任重道遠。", "name": "太空鱗獸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2040_1#1$3"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#4$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "該死，聽證會到底還開不開？要是讓我來負責，事情早就解決了！那個老東西就是故意陷害我，七年前是這樣，現在還是這樣！", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#7$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你為什麼七年以來毫無長進？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "古斯塔夫長官……", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#6$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodfloor_fts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2042_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2042_1#1$1", "focus": "r", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說吧，如果是你，打算怎麼處理？", "name": "古斯塔夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2042_1#1$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這……", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#6$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2042_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊茵的工程檢修終止了就沾沾自喜，以為自己可以從此高枕無憂地繼續做見不得人的小生意……", "name": "古斯塔夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2042_1#8$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2042_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "管理局又不是幼稚園，怎麼把你培養得如此天真？", "name": "古斯塔夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2042_1#7$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要不是那棵該死的樹，本來一切都很順利，都怪娜斯提！", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#7$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2042_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "順利？你知不知道娜斯提手下的一個助理研究員都能看穿你的把戲？", "name": "古斯塔夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2042_1#6$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2042_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要不是他跟你一樣天真，向我尋求幫助，你的醜事早就被公之於眾了。", "name": "古斯塔夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2042_1#8$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#6$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2042_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說啊，你打算怎麼處理？", "name": "古斯塔夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2042_1#8$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長官……請您幫我……", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#4$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2042_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼。不管萊茵隱瞞這件浮空裝置是出於什麼樣的目的，我們都不能讓他們繼續掌控自己的造物。", "name": "古斯塔夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2042_1#8$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2042_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為你的失職，本來可以全權接手的行政部一概不能參與評估。", "name": "古斯塔夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2042_1#4$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您的意思是，我們需要引入“第三方”？", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#8$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2042_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一名客觀、專業、看起來中立的科學顧問。", "name": "古斯塔夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2042_1#1$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodfloor_fts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2038_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 2.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高登先生，久仰大名。", "name": "科學顧問"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2038_1#1$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2042_1#1$1", "focus": "l", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他長得一點也不像科學顧問……他真的能處理萊茵的東西？", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#9$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2038_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了熟悉我的評估對象，剛剛我去了一趟浮空平台。", "name": "科學顧問"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2038_1#1$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2038_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，真是極為壯觀的一棵“巨木”，就連“樹”下也很熱鬧。", "name": "科學顧問"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2038_1#2$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "68_g9_treeplatform_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1", "duration": 0.8, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來啊！有本事就從我們的屍體上跨過去！", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#6$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（斯凱先生……）", "name": "體驗員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（怕什麼，嚇嚇他而已。）", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊茵的科學家是不是被星莢外面的輻射照壞腦子了，你偏要有人流血才善罷甘休？", "name": "園區警衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然如此，我就成全你！", "name": "園區警衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "住手。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodfloor_fts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1", "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1", "duration": 0.8, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.8}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這身制服……你們是梅蘭德的人？", "name": "園區警衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1", "focus": "r", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們是梅蘭德基金會旗下的緊急管理監督協會成員。根據園區守則，在事故與災害發生時，本機構將全權接管行政和管理職能。", "name": "協會成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您可以向高登長官和古斯塔夫先生確認。", "name": "協會成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "園區警衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#5$1", "posfrom": "80,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.8, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "監督協會？", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#5$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，斯凱先生。", "name": "協會成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們十分理解您的心情，但請不要做出過激舉動，我們有權對您和您的同伴採取強制措施。", "name": "協會成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以“螺旋槳天堂”確實進入了緊急狀態，昨天晚上的事件在你們的初步調查中被定調為——“特殊事故”？", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯。監督協會已經成立特殊調查組，對現場和涉事人員進行取證。", "name": "協會成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的調查工作還在繼續，在缺少官方司法監督機構的情況下，舉行聽證會是唯一公正的審理手段，希望各位能夠耐心等待。", "name": "協會成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}, {"id": 407, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在聽證會召開之前，萊茵是否保有這件“浮空種植單元”的所有權？", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。", "name": "協會成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}, {"id": 411, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望你們的調查結果，會跟剛剛你給我的結論一樣公正。", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請您放心。", "name": "協會成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}, {"id": 415, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "臨時浮空平台確認安全，二組繼續巡邏。", "name": "協會成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}, {"id": 421, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodfloor_fts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.8, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1", "duration": 0.8, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.8}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯凱先生，我們就這樣走了？", "name": "體驗員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從警衛的態度來看，梅蘭德的管轄權是貨真價實的。", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1"}, {"id": 433, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽證會的時間一拖再拖，說不定還會發生什麼變數，在這裡等下去無益於我們掌握情報，還有……", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 435, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們有人看到娜斯提主任嗎？", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 437, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}